31#ifndef _THREAD_POOL_H_
32#define _THREAD_POOL_H_
33
34#pragma ident "%Z%%M% %I% %E% SMI"
35
36#include <sys/types.h>
37#include <thread.h>
38#include <pthread.h>
39
40#ifdef __cplusplus
41extern "C" {
42#endif
43
44typedef struct tpool tpool_t; /* opaque thread pool descriptor */
45
46#if defined(__STDC__)
47
48extern tpool_t *tpool_create(uint_t min_threads, uint_t max_threads,
49 uint_t linger, pthread_attr_t *attr);
50extern int tpool_dispatch(tpool_t *tpool,
51 void (*func)(void *), void *arg);
52extern void tpool_destroy(tpool_t *tpool);
53extern void tpool_abandon(tpool_t *tpool);
54extern void tpool_wait(tpool_t *tpool);
55extern void tpool_suspend(tpool_t *tpool);
56extern int tpool_suspended(tpool_t *tpool);
57extern void tpool_resume(tpool_t *tpool);
58extern int tpool_member(tpool_t *tpool);
59
60#else /* Non ANSI */
61
62extern tpool_t *tpool_create();
63extern int tpool_dispatch();
64extern void tpool_destroy();
65extern void tpool_abandon();
66extern void tpool_wait();
67extern void tpool_suspend();
68extern int tpool_suspended();
69extern void tpool_resume();
70extern int tpool_member();
71
72#endif /* __STDC__ */
73
74#ifdef __cplusplus
75}
76#endif
77
78#endif /* _THREAD_POOL_H_ */
79
